d</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If you&rsquo;re responsible for part or all of the clean up, you can agree a voluntary scheme with your <a href=\"/find-your-local-council\" title=\"Find your local council\">local council</a>. You must tell them what steps you will take to clean up the land. </p>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/contaminated-land/developing-land","slug":"developing-land","order":4,"title":"Developing land","body":"<p>You could have to clean up land contamination on your site before you can develop it. </p>\n\n<p>Contact your <a href=\"/find-your-local-council\" title=\"Find your local council\">local council</a> to discuss planning and to check what you must do to make sure the land is suitable for your proposed development. </p>\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/contaminated-land/buying-contaminated-land","slug":"buying-contaminated-land","order":5,"title":"Buying contaminated land","body":"<p>If you&rsquo;re buying contaminated land, you could get financial help to clean it up and make sure it is suitable for use. </p>\n\n<p>You could get:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>capital allowances</li>\n  <li>an exemption from stamp duty</li>\n  <li>enhanced tax relief</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Read about financial help you could get on the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/manuals/cirdmanual/CIRD60000.htm\" title=\"Read about financial help you could get on the HM Revenue &amp; Customs website\">HM Revenue &amp; Customs website.</a></p>\n"}]},"updated_at":"2012-11-09T17:15:57+00:00","tags":[{"title":"Waste and environmental impact","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business%2Fwaste-environment.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes waste management plans, hazardous waste and preventing pollution","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business%2Fwaste-environment","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business/waste-environment"},"parent":{"title":"Businesses and self-employed","id